'''2013年[[MTV音乐录影带大奖|MTV音乐录影带大奖]]'''颁奖典礼于2013年8月25日在[[美国|美国]][[纽约|纽约]][[布鲁克林|布鲁克林]]的[[巴克萊中心|巴克萊中心]]举行<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.mtv.com/news/articles/1704268/vmas-2013-brooklyn-barclays-center.jhtml |title=MTV VMAs Coming To Brooklyn's Barclays Center! - Music, Celebrity, Artist News |last=Kaufman |first=Gil |date=July 17, 2012 |work=[[MTV|MTV]] |publisher=[[Viacom|Viacom]] |accessdate=July 18, 2013 |archive-date=2013-10-23 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131023112942/http://www.mtv.com/news/articles/1704268/vmas-2013-brooklyn-barclays-center.jhtml |dead-url=no }}</ref>。提名于2013年7月17日公布，其中[[贾斯汀·汀布莱克|贾斯汀·汀布莱克]]、[[Macklemore|Macklemore]]与[[瑞恩·刘易斯|瑞恩·刘易斯]]各获得6项提名领先其他艺人，其次是[[布鲁诺·马尔斯|布鲁诺·马尔斯]]、[[麦莉·赛勒斯|麦莉·赛勒斯]]和[[罗宾·西克|罗宾·西克]]各获得4项提名。<ref>{{citeweb|url= http://www.dailymail.co.uk/tvshowbiz/article-2402006/Its-strip-Katy-Perry-Lady-Gaga-Miley-Cyrus-perform-smalls-fight-limelight-sexed-MTV-VMAs-2013.html|title= It’s not a strip show! Katy Perry, Lady Gaga and Miley Cyrus perform in their smalls as they fight for the limelight on sexed up MTV VMAs 2013|date= 25 August 2013|work= Daily Mail|accessdate= 26 August 2013|archive-date= 2019-09-11|archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20190911213119/https://www.dailymail.co.uk/tvshowbiz/article-2402006/MTV-VMAs-2013-Katy-Perry-Lady-Gaga-Miley-Cyrus-perform-underwear.html|dead-url= no}}</ref><ref>{{citeweb|url= http://www.nytimes.com/2013/08/27/arts/music/mtv-video-music-awards-review.html?hp|title= At Video Music Awards, a Lot to Look Away From|date= 26 August 2013|work= New York Times|accessdate= 26 August 2013|archive-date= 2013-08-29|archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20130829063745/http://www.nytimes.com/2013/08/27/arts/music/mtv-video-music-awards-review.html?hp|dead-url= no}}</ref>
颁奖典礼上最受瞩目的瞬间是[[麦莉·赛勒斯|麦莉·赛勒斯]]和[[罗宾·西克|罗宾·西克]]的表演。两人共同表演了各自的热门单曲《We Can't Stop》和《Blurred Lines》，表演尺度较大且极富性暗示意味，引发评论界及观众的不满和负面评价。仅[[美国联邦通信委员会|美国联邦通信委员会]]就收到超过150条投诉意见。<ref>{{cite news|last=Nordyke|first=Kimberly|title=FCC Flooded With Complaints Over Miley Cyrus' Racy VMA Performance|url=http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/live-feed/miley-cyrus-twerking-vma-performance-629645|accessdate=16 September 2013|newspaper=[[The_Hollywood_Reporter|The Hollywood Reporter]]|date=September 15, 2013|archive-date=2020-08-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200821132313/https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/live-feed/miley-cyrus-twerking-vma-performance-629645|dead-url=no}}</ref>颁奖典礼另一个备受关注的时刻是[[贾斯汀·汀布莱克|贾斯汀·汀布莱克]]获得“[[迈克尔·杰克逊音乐录影带先锋奖|迈克尔·杰克逊音乐录影带先锋奖]]”之后与[[超级男孩|超级男孩]]在2002年解散之后首次同台演出。

